 {"id":"bd-mblr.4.1.2","title":"Scenario traceability map (test <-> scenario <-> artifact)","description":"Map each scenario ID to concrete tests/runners and expected artifacts/log events. Output: traceability table enabling coverage and diagnostics audits.","design":"Generate map automatically from manifests and test metadata where possible; manual exceptions must be explicit.","acceptance_criteria":"- Traceability table maps test names/scripts to scenario IDs and expected artifact set.
