 {"id":"bd-mblr.4.2","title":"Implement Missing E2E Scenarios from Matrix","description":"Implement test scripts/suites for uncovered scenarios identified in the canonical matrix. Prioritize correctness and reliability scenarios before perf-only expansions.","design":"Implement scenarios through shared runner abstractions to keep seed handling, logging, and artifact capture consistent.","acceptance_criteria":"- Uncovered scenarios from matrix are implemented as deterministic scripts/tests with explicit oracles.
