 {"id":"bd-mblr.4.2.1","title":"Implement missing transaction/recovery scenarios","description":"Add missing E2E scenarios for transactional edges, rollback/commit ordering, savepoints, and crash/recovery paths. Output: new deterministic scenario tests with expected-state validation.","design":"Use table-driven transaction scripts with deterministic checkpoints to isolate failure cause quickly.","acceptance_criteria":"- Transaction/recovery scenarios cover rollback/commit ordering, savepoints, and crash/reopen paths.
- Each scenario validates expected final state and invariant IDs, not just command success.
